title: Coral Reef Spawning, Worldwide
name: Coral Reef Spawning, Worldwide
description: The ReefBase Coral Spawning dataset provides observation details of coral spawning occurrences around the world. Main sources of information for this dataset have been: published records from the literature, postings on the coral-list(http://www.coral.noaa.gov/lists/).This data was found online at http://www.reefbase.org/gis_maps/download.aspx.
